descript.abstract: This data set represents the liquefaction potential for Box Elder, Cache, Davis, Salt Lake, Utah and Weber Counties.
descript.purpose: To show the liquefaction potential for Box Elder, Cache, Davis, Salt Lake, Utah and Weber Countiesl.
descript.supplinf: The maps were digitized by Janine Jarva, Utah Geological Survey (UGS), from original mylars provided by Loren Anderson of Utah State University (USU). The maps were published in four UGS Contract Reports in 1994.
